in 1999 by the lead role in Bhopal Express,  a movie that went mostly unnoticed. This was the first in a series of  initial setbacks in Menon's film career. In the early 2000s, he starred  as a wicked rock musician in Anurag Kashyap's debut movie, Paanch, which struggled with censorship and has remained unreleased. Two other movies, Hazaaron Khwaishein Aisi and Black Friday, had to wait many years for a release date. Meanwhile, his commercial films Deewar (starring Amitabh Bachchan) and Silsiilay (with Shahrukh Khan) flopped at the box office. It was only in 2005, with the eventual release of the critically acclaimed Hazaaron Khwaishein Aisi, but most of all with Ram Gopal Varma's Sarkar, that Menon had his break. Sarkar earned him a nomination for the Best Performance in a Negative Role at the Filmfare Awards. In The Tribune, Saibal Chatterjee called him \"one of Bollywood's finest actors\".","name":"Kay Kay Menon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Kay Kay Menon ist ein indischer Film-, Bühnen- und Fernsehschauspieler, der überwiegend im Hindi-Kino arbeitet. Menon debütierte mit einer kleinen Rolle in Naseem (1995), gefolgt von der Hauptrolle in Bhopal Express, einem Film, der weitgehend unbemerkt blieb. Dies war der erste in einer Reihe von ersten Rückschlägen in Menons Filmkarriere.\n\nIn den frühen 2000er Jahren spielte er als böser Rockmusiker in Anurag Kashyaps Debütfilm Paanch, der mit der Zensur kämpfte und unveröffentlicht blieb. Zwei weitere Filme, Hazaaron Khwaishein Aisi und Black Friday, mussten viele Jahre auf einen Veröffentlichungstermin warten. Inzwischen fielen seine Werbefilme Deewar (mit Amitabh Bachchan) und Silsiilay (mit Shahrukh Khan) an der Abendkasse.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kay Kay Menon","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凯·凯·门农","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"קיי קיי מנון","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凱·凱·門農","primary":false}}]}}}}